<body>



<div style="min-height:100vh;">

  <nav style="position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; background:#1F7A4D; padding:0 1.75rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; height:56px;">
    <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:#EAF5EE;">iman<b style="color:#7EDCA8;">naeem</b></span>
    <ul style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0;">
      <li><a href="#tsauditor" class="hov1">TSAuditor</a></li>
      <li><a href="#projects" class="hov2">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#oss" class="hov3">Open Source</a></li>
      <li><a href="#skills" class="hov4">Skills</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/imann128" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov5">GitHub</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <main style="max-width:1040px; margin:0 auto; padding:2.5rem 1.75rem 4rem;">

    <section style="text-align:center; padding:3rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;">
      <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; color:#1F7A4D; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; margin:0 0 0.9rem;">NUST SEECS, Islamabad</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Noto Serif',Georgia,serif; font-size:clamp(2.6rem,6vw,4rem); line-height:1.02; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin:0 0 1.25rem;">Iman Naeem</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.1rem; color:#3A4F44; max-width:680px; margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
        I work primarily in data analytics and engineering, building dashboards, extracting insights, and designing
        pipelines to understand what's really happening at the data level. A lot of my work takes a Pakistan-centric
        angle, like my <em style="color:#1F7A4D; font-style:italic;">OGDC equity-analysis platform</em> built on 6+ years
        of PSX stock data. I build end-to-end data systems spanning ETL, statistical inference, and machine learning,
        and full-stack apps across Python, .NET, and React backed by SQLite, Redis, and PostgreSQL. Most of my focus
        right now is <em style="color:#1F7A4D; font-style:italic;">open source</em>: I authored <em style="color:#1F7A4D; font-style:italic;">TSAuditor</em>,
        a time-series data-quality library now on PyPI, and landed a merged contribution to <em style="color:#1F7A4D; font-style:italic;">statsmodels</em>,
        both rooted in one thing I care about: making sure data is trustworthy before anyone models it.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.6rem;">
        <a href="https://github.com/imann128" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov6">github.com/imann128</a>
        <a href="https://dev.to/imann_12" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov7">dev.to/imann_12</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tsauditor" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:500; color:#1F7A4D; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; white-space:nowrap;">Featured Open-Source Library</span>
        <div style="flex:1; height:1px; background:#DCE5DA;"></div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #DCE5DA; border-radius:18px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(20,83,45,.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(20,83,45,.05); display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.05fr 0.95fr;">

        <div style="padding:2.1rem 2.2rem;">
          <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1F7A4D; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; border-radius:999px; padding:4px 11px; margin-bottom:1.1rem;">
            <span style="width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:#1F7A4D; display:inline-block;"></span> Live on PyPI, community-backed
          </span>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif; font-weight:600; font-size:1.85rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 0.4rem; letter-spacing:-0.01em; color:#142420;">TSAuditor
            <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12px; font-weight:400; color:#6C8177; display:block; margin-top:5px; letter-spacing:0;">a time-series integrity &amp; data-quality auditing framework</span>
          </h2>
          <p style="color:#3A4F44; font-size:14.5px; margin:0 0 0.9rem; font-weight:600;">tsauditor 0.2.0, the data guard release</p>
          <p style="color:#3A4F44; font-size:14.5px; margin:0 0 1.1rem;">
            A major, fully backward-compatible feature release. TSAuditor moves from a leakage detector toward a
            complete data guard: it now catches point-in-time and validity flaws, repairs them on a copy, scores
            data health, exports formal reports, and hands clean arrays straight to forecasting models.
          </p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.4rem; margin-bottom:1.2rem;">
            <span style="font-size:11.5px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:#EAF5EE; color:#1F7A4D; border:1px solid #CFE8D8;">Leakage detection (AUC-based)</span>
            <span style="font-size:11.5px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:#EAF5EE; color:#1F7A4D; border:1px solid #CFE8D8;">Point-in-time &amp; validity checks</span>
            <span style="font-size:11.5px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:#EAF5EE; color:#1F7A4D; border:1px solid #CFE8D8;">Auto-repair on a copy</span>
            <span style="font-size:11.5px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:#EAF5EE; color:#1F7A4D; border:1px solid #CFE8D8;">Data-health scoring</span>
            <span style="font-size:11.5px; font-weight:500; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background:#EAF5EE; color:#1F7A4D; border:1px solid #CFE8D8;">Rich + JSON reports</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-style:italic; font-size:13px; color:#6C8177; margin-bottom:1.3rem;">Featured in Data Science Weekly, Substack Issue 657, plus mentions across numerous tech blogs.</p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.6rem;">
            <a href="https://github.com/imann128/tsauditor" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov8">↗ GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://pypi.org/project/tsauditor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov9">↗ PyPI</a>
            <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/MachineLearning/comments/1ub15wf/tsauditor_a_timeseries_auditing_framework_p/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov10">↗ r/MachineLearning</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; background:#EAF5EE; height:100%;">
          <div style="background:#123524; color:#fff; padding:1.5rem 1.6rem;">
            <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:0.95rem;">tsauditor 0.2.0</div>
            <span style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:9px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:12.5px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28); border-radius:8px; padding:8px 13px;">pip install tsauditor</span>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; margin-top:1rem; color:#CFE8D8;">
              <b style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:#2c9b3f; color:#fff; border:none; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:6px; font-weight:500;">Latest release</b> Released Jul 5, 2026
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:1.4rem 1.6rem; flex:1;">
            <div style="font-size:12.5px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:1.1rem;">A data guard for time-series tabular data in financial and sensor domains. Version 0.2.0 catches point-in-time and validity flaws, repairs them on a copy, scores data health, and exports formal reports. Fully backward-compatible. CI green across Python 3.9 to 3.14 on Linux, Windows &amp; macOS.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.45rem;">
              <span style="display:inline-flex; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; border-radius:5px; overflow:hidden;"><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#3a3a3a; color:#fff;">CI</span><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#3f9c35; color:#fff;">passing</span></span>
              <span style="display:inline-flex; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; border-radius:5px; overflow:hidden;"><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#3a3a3a; color:#fff;">codecov</span><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#5b9c35; color:#fff;">90%</span></span>
              <span style="display:inline-flex; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; border-radius:5px; overflow:hidden;"><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#3a3a3a; color:#fff;">license</span><span style="padding:3px 9px; background:#b5852a; color:#fff;">MIT</span></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="projects" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.85rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; font-weight:500; color:#1F7A4D; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; white-space:nowrap;">Selected Projects</span>
        <div style="flex:1; height:1px; background:#DCE5DA;"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.25rem;">

        <div style="border:1px solid #CFE8D8; background:#EAF5EE; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(20,83,45,.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(20,83,45,.05); display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
          <div style="background:#1E1E1E; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
            <div style="padding:8px 12px 6px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px;"><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#FF5F57;"></div><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#FFBD2E;"></div><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#28CA42;"></div></div>
            <img src="assets/cfd13ad5-8ead-4de1-8162-35a1db32d95a.png" alt="OGDC equity analysis dashboard" style="width:100%; display:block; height:188px; object-fit:cover; object-position:top;">
          </div>
          <div style="padding:1.1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
            <div style="font-size:14.5px; font-weight:600; color:#142420; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">OGDC Equity Analysis Platform</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.55; margin-bottom:0.9rem; flex:1;">End-to-end pipeline over 6+ years of PSX data: GARCH volatility modelling, Bollinger-Band backtesting, and sentiment analysis across 14 sources, surfaced through a deployed React dashboard. Built with strict train/test discipline to avoid look-ahead leakage.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.35rem; margin-bottom:0.9rem;">
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Python</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">React.js</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">GARCH</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Recharts</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Vercel</span>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex; gap:0.85rem;">
              <a href="https://github.com/imann128/ogdc-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov11">↗ GitHub</a>
              <a href="https://ogdc-project.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hov12">↗ Live</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="border:1px solid #DCE5DA; background:#FFFFFF; border-radius:14px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(20,83,45,.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(20,83,45,.05); display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
          <div style="background:#1E1E1E; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
            <div style="padding:8px 12px 6px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:5px;"><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#FF5F57;"></div><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#FFBD2E;"></div><div style="width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:#28CA42;"></div></div>
            <img src="assets/59575470-b873-4833-a7c3-7ebfd1c27980.png" alt="IoT anomaly detection dashboard" style="width:100%; display:block; height:188px; object-fit:cover; object-position:top;">
          </div>
          <div style="padding:1.1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
            <div style="font-size:14.5px; font-weight:600; color:#142420; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">IoT Sensor Anomaly Detection Pipeline</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.55; margin-bottom:0.9rem; flex:1;">Dual-method anomaly detection on NASA SMAP/MSL telemetry: Isolation Forest and a z-score rolling window, benchmarked against labelled ground truth with precision/recall reported per channel. Containerised for reproducible runs.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.35rem; margin-bottom:0.9rem;">
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Python</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Isolation Forest</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">LSTM</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Docker</span>
