            <img src="assets/34ccca79-610e-4862-b699-2a62c42960b3.png" alt="DevMetrics dashboard" style="width:100%; display:block; height:188px; object-fit:cover; object-position:top;">
          </div>
          <div style="padding:1.1rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
            <div style="font-size:14.5px; font-weight:600; color:#142420; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">DevMetrics</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.55; margin-bottom:0.9rem; flex:1;">Self-hosted Git activity monitor with closed-loop telemetry. Streams live commit data over SignalR, computes craftsmanship signals, and exposes a Prometheus-compatible <code>/metrics</code> endpoint for dashboards and alerting.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.35rem; margin-bottom:0.9rem;">
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">.NET 8</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">SignalR</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">OpenAPI 3.0</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Prometheus</span>
              <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:500; padding:2px 8px; border-radius:5px; background:#EAF5EE; border:1px solid #CFE8D8; color:#1F7A4D;">Docker</span>
