            <div style="font-size:13px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.55; margin-bottom:0.9rem; flex:1;">Production webhook relay with at-least-once delivery, Redis-backed idempotent deduplication, JSONPath fan-out routing, HMAC-SHA256 verification, an SSRF guard, and a dead-letter queue for failed deliveries.</div>
            <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.35rem; margin-bottom:0.9rem;">
