            <div style="font-size:13px; color:#3A4F44; line-height:1.55; margin-bottom:0.9rem; flex:1;">Product-intelligence dashboard over 50K generation events, answering five business questions: which model ships, where latency costs retention, quality trends, optimal prompt length, and keyword-quality correlation.</div>
